  <brief_title>Prospective Evaluation of the Proceed Ventral Patch With and Without Laparoscopic Evaluation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicentric Evaluation of the Proceed Ventral Patch for Umbilical and Small Primary Ventral Hernias Less Than 3cm Diameter With One Year Follow-up</official_title>
